---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  structuredDataType="WebPage"
  structuredData={{
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Small Business SEO Guide 2025",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    }
  }}
>
  <Header />
  
  <Hero 
    headline="Small Business <span class='text-yellow-400'>SEO Guide</span> for 2025"
    subheadline="Practical SEO strategies that actually work for local businesses. No fluff, just results."
    primaryCTA={{
      text: "Get SEO Help Now",
      href: "/contact"
    }}
    secondaryCTA={{
      text: "See Our SEO Results",
      href: "/services/seo-services"
    }}
  />

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          SEO for small businesses isn't the same as SEO for large corporations. You need strategies that work 
          for local markets, limited budgets, and real business goals. This guide focuses on practical, 
          proven tactics that help small businesses get found by local customers.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Whether you're a restaurant in Wilmington, a contractor in Charlotte, or a service business anywhere in North Carolina, 
          these strategies will help you outrank competitors and attract more customers through search engines.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <i data-lucide="lightbulb" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                <strong>Reality Check:</strong> 97% of consumers search online to find local businesses. 
                If you're not showing up in those searches, you're invisible to potential customers.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Foundations -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6 SEO Foundations Every Small Business Needs</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Master these fundamentals before worrying about advanced tactics. These basics drive 80% of your SEO success.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={seoFoundations} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local SEO Deep Dive -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Google My Business Optimization</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Your Google My Business profile is often a customer's first impression. Here's how to make it count.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Complete Your Profile 100%</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Essential Information:</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• Exact business name (no keywords stuffing)</li>
                <li>• Complete address with suite numbers</li>
                <li>• Primary phone number (local preferred)</li>
                <li>• Accurate business hours including holidays</li>
                <li>• Primary and secondary business categories</li>
                <li>• Professional business description</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Enhanced Features:</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                <li>• High-quality photos (interior, exterior, team)</li>
                <li>• Regular posts and updates</li>
                <li>• Q&A section management</li>
                <li>• Services or products listings</li>
                <li>• Booking links when applicable</li>
                <li>• Messaging enabled for customer questions</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-8">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Review Management Strategy</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Reviews are one of the strongest local ranking factors. Here's how to build a steady stream of positive reviews:
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ask Strategically</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Request reviews from happy customers immediately after positive interactions or successful project completion.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Respond to All</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Reply to every review professionally. Thank positive reviewers and address concerns from negative reviews constructively.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Make it Easy</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Provide direct links to your review profiles. The easier it is, the more reviews you'll get from satisfied customers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Strategy -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Local Content That Ranks and Converts</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Content marketing for local SEO is about answering customer questions and targeting location-based searches.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={contentStrategies} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical SEO -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Technical SEO Basics for Small Business</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Technical SEO doesn't have to be complicated. Focus on these fundamentals to ensure Google can find and understand your site.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={technicalSEO} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Local Link Building -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Local Link Building Strategies</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Build authority and trust with Google through local partnerships and community involvement.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={localSEOTactics} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitor Analysis -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Competitive Analysis for Local SEO</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Understanding your competition helps you identify opportunities and develop winning strategies.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={competitorAnalysis} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Timeline Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Realistic SEO Timeline & Expectations</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          SEO is a long-term investment. Here's what to expect month by month.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">0-3</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Months 0-3: Foundation & Setup</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Focus on technical fixes, Google My Business optimization, and initial content creation. 
              You may see small improvements in local search visibility.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Expected Results:</strong> Better local visibility, improved Google My Business engagement, technical issues resolved</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 font-bold text-lg">3-6</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Months 3-6: Growth & Momentum</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Content starts ranking, local citations build authority, and you begin to see consistent traffic growth 
              for targeted keywords.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Expected Results:</strong> 20-40% increase in organic traffic, improved keyword rankings, more customer inquiries</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600 font-bold text-lg">6-12</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Months 6-12: Competitive Positioning</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Established authority leads to higher rankings for competitive terms. Your business becomes a 
              go-to choice for local customers in your industry.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Expected Results:</strong> 50-100% increase in organic traffic, top 3 rankings for key terms, measurable business growth</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 font-bold text-lg">12+</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">12+ Months: Market Dominance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Sustained efforts result in market-leading positions. Your business is the first choice for 
              local customers and generates consistent leads from search.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Expected Results:</strong> Market-leading organic visibility, consistent lead generation, strong brand recognition</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Measurement & Tools -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Measuring Your SEO Success</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Track the right metrics to understand your SEO performance and make data-driven decisions.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={measurementTools} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Action Plan -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your 30-Day SEO Action Plan</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Start with these high-impact activities to see immediate improvements in your local search presence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Week 1: Google My Business Optimization</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Complete your Google My Business profile 100%</li>
              <li>• Add high-quality photos of your business</li>
              <li>• Write a compelling business description</li>
              <li>• Set up messaging and Q&A sections</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Week 2: Technical Foundation</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Audit your website for mobile responsiveness</li>
              <li>• Check page loading speeds with Google PageSpeed Insights</li>
              <li>• Ensure your site has SSL security</li>
              <li>• Set up Google Analytics and Search Console</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Week 3: Content & Keywords</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Research keywords your customers use to find businesses like yours</li>
              <li>• Optimize your homepage title and description</li>
              <li>• Create one location-based service page</li>
              <li>• Write your first blog post answering a common customer question</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-500 pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Week 4: Citations & Reviews</h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>• Create profiles on major directories (Yelp, Yellow Pages, etc.)</li>
              <li>• Ensure your NAP is consistent everywhere</li>
              <li>• Ask your best customers for Google reviews</li>
              <li>• Respond to any existing reviews professionally</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <CTASection 
    headline="Ready to Dominate Local Search Results?"
    description="Let us handle your SEO while you focus on running your business. Get a free SEO audit and strategy session."
    primaryCTA={{
      text: "Get Your Free SEO Audit",
      href: "/contact"
    }}
    secondaryCTA={{
      text: "See Our SEO Case Studies",
      href: "/services/seo-services"
    }}
  />

  <Footer />
</Layout>

